# User Stories - School Management System

## User Roles
- **Admin**: System administrator
- **Teacher**: School teacher
- **Student**: Student
- **Parent**: Parent of a student

---

## Admin User Stories (Done)

**US-ADMIN-01** - ✅ Done
> As an **admin**, I want to authenticate with my credentials to access the back-office.
> *Acceptance Criteria: Login form with validation, redirect to `/admin` after success, error messages for invalid credentials.*

**US-ADMIN-02** - ✅ Done
> As an **admin**, I want to view key metrics (students, teachers, parents count) to have an overview of the institution.
> *Acceptance Criteria: Statistics cards on dashboard, real-time aggregated data from PostgreSQL.*

**US-ADMIN-03** - ✅ Done
> As an **admin**, I want to view the complete student list with their information (ID, name, class, email, phone) to manage enrollments.
> *Acceptance Criteria: Paginated table with relevant columns, link to each student's detailed page.*

**US-ADMIN-04** - ✅ Done
> As an **admin**, I want to search for a student by name to quickly access their information.
> *Acceptance Criteria: Search field with real-time filtering.*

**US-ADMIN-05** - ⏳ In Progress
> As an **admin**, I want to add a new student via a form to register them in the system.
> *Acceptance Criteria: Form with field validation, database save via Prisma, instant display in the list.*

---

## Teacher User Stories

**US-TEACH-01** - ⏳ In Progress
> As a **teacher**, I want to view the list of students in my class to track their results.
> *Acceptance Criteria: Automatic filtering by class, grades display by subject.*

**US-TEACH-02** - 📋 Planned
> As a **teacher**, I want to enter or modify a student's grades to update their report card.
> *Acceptance Criteria: Grade entry form by subject, automatic average calculation update.*

**US-TEACH-03** - 📋 Planned
> As a **teacher**, I want to mark daily attendance to track student presence.
> *Acceptance Criteria: Interactive calendar, attendance statistics per student.*

---

## Student User Stories (Final)

**US-STUD-01** - 📋 Planned
> As a **student**, I want to log in and view my report card (subjects, coefficients, average) to track my progress.

**US-STUD-02** - 📋 Planned
> As a **student**, I want to view my weekly schedule to organize my work.

---

## Parent User Stories (Final)

**US-PARENT-01** - 📋 Planned
> As a **parent**, I want to access my child's grades and attendance to follow their academic progress.

